text:
Very reasonably priced mixed vege stall. Offers both porridge and rice. Great supper spot with wide variety of dishes. Coffeeshop still bustling with life even late at night.

Tip: order one person serving even if you are sharing so you can get more dishes :)
Cheap mixed rice but the aunty taking my food has a very bad attitude. She got angry when she couldnâ€™t hear / see the food I was pointing at, even mumble words about me to the guy beside her.
Usually quite food for their chicken wings. However the guy wearing glass gave me the egg which fell on the table was terrible.
